###MyBrowserPage is a starterpage with Metro design, graphical list of most popular sites and multiple search engine included,…

MyBrowserPage is a starterpage with Metro design, graphical list of most popular websites and multiple search engine included, personal bookmarks, free to use.

You can add MBP to your default Homepage.

https://mybrowserpage.com
